perimental measurements on magnetically confined\nplasmas. The statistical framework defines a new validation metric for boundary\nturbulence simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2021 09:33:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2021 08:07:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-28"}
